<rms:rms_experience_0_description>Working as a Front-End Developer on a 3-Tier Architecture project, building scalable and user-friendly interfaces.&#xA;Developing and maintaining four portals (DKYC, DMS, and API-driven platforms) with responsive UI designs.&#xA;Implementing features using React.js, Next.js, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap, and Tailwind CSS.&#xA;Ensuring seamless user experience through performance optimization and cross-platform compatibility.</rms:rms_experience_0_description>
