<rms:rms_experience_1_description>Designed DKYC and CKYC portals with full desktop and mobile responsiveness.&#xA;Built user-friendly UI ensuring smooth access across all devices.&#xA;Ensured compliance and performance in cross-platform portal design.</rms:rms_experience_1_description>
