<rms:rms_experience_2_description>Designed and developed the company's first official website, establishing an online presence.&#xA;Created a fully responsive design, improving mobile compatibility by 100%.&#xA;Enhanced user experience with intuitive navigation, increasing engagement.&#xA;Integrated a dynamic contact form with real-time email notifications, improving response time.</rms:rms_experience_2_description>
