<rms:rms_summary>Full Stack Developer with strong expertise in Frontend development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Bootstrap) and practical experience in Backend technologies (ASP.NET Core, MySQL, Python). Skilled in building responsive, user-friendly, and scalable web applications (DKYC &amp; CKYC), with a focus on UI/UX, cross-platform compatibility, and continuous growth in full stack development.</rms:rms_summary>
